The Source.java file has two unresolved imports for the classes OutputFormat and
XMLSerializer
The following 2 imports are not resolved in the Source.java file:

import org.apache.xml.serialize.OutputFormat;
import org.apache.xml.serialize.XMLSerializer;

Organizing the imports (ctrl-shift o), changes these to:

import com.sun.org.apache.xml.internal.serialize.OutputFormat;
import com.sun.org.apache.xml.internal.serialize.XMLSerializer;

which do resolve the class imports correctly.

